  "excerpt": "<p>Each Marketplace application has a unique identification number or application ID (sometimes called just an \u201cAPP ID\u201d or \u201cID\u201d).</p>",
  "content": "<p>Each Marketplace application has a unique identification number or application ID (sometimes called just an \u201cAPP ID\u201d or \u201cID\u201d).</p><p><strong>Note</strong>: Your application ID is different from <a href=\"/help/how-do-i-find-my-plan-id\" data-entity-type=\"node\" data-entity-uuid=\"20370c28-5608-4a9e-86b3-583a4648b37c\" data-entity-substitution=\"canonical\" data-entity-id=\"38566\" data-entity-bundle=\"article\" title=\"How do I find my plan ID?\">your plan ID</a>.</p><h2>2 ways to find your application ID</h2><h3>1. Online:</h3><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\" data-align=\"center\">\n  \n      \n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\">\n    <div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"550\" data-image-height=\"430\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/en/application-id.png?itok=PfnHYV8S 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/en/application-id.png?itok=eGn6VCLH 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/application-id.png?itok=K50ggS9G 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"801\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/application-id.png?itok=K50ggS9G\" alt=\"{This is how you find your application ID.}\" title=\"{This is how you find your application ID.}\">\n\n\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-spanish-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image-es media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image-spanish field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"550\" data-image-height=\"430\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/es/application-id.png?itok=2EvR6SVI 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/es/application-id.png?itok=lnAJIXZA 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/application-id.png?itok=8R5HWSUa 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"801\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/application-id.png?itok=8R5HWSUa\" alt>\n\n\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n<p>&nbsp;</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://www.healthcare.gov/login\">Log into your Marketplace account.</a></li><li>Under \"Your applications,\" the application ID (ID#) is in the middle.</li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>2. In your eligibility notice:</h3><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default\" data-align=\"center\">\n  \n      \n  <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\">\n    <div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div>\n              <div class=\"field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"589\" data-image-height=\"767\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/en/app-id-notice.png?itok=tNmyRrVl 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/en/app-id-notice.png?itok=U7j1UCQY 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/app-id-notice.png?itok=B83QdeUY 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1333\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/en/app-id-notice.png?itok=B83QdeUY\" alt=\"{This is your application ID number.\" title=\"{This is your application ID number.\">\n\n\n</div>\n          </div>\n\n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-spanish-image field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image-es media--view-mode-default\">\n  \n      \n            <div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image-spanish field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\">    <img loading=\"eager\" data-image-encoded=\"data:image/png;base64,\" data-image-width=\"589\" data-image-height=\"767\" srcset=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_small_544/public/inline-images/es/app-id-notice.png?itok=oIDUZTnx 544w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_medium_768/public/inline-images/es/app-id-notice.png?itok=SHj7fRgw 768w, /sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/app-id-notice.png?itok=Y-Hz9Y34 1024w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 1290px) 1290px, 100vw\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1333\" src=\"/sites/default/files/styles/gatsby_large_1024/public/inline-images/es/app-id-notice.png?itok=Y-Hz9Y34\" alt>\n\n\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n</div>\n      \n  </article>\n<p>Look for your \"Application ID\" at the top of your Eligibility Notice. You'll get this notice after you submit your application. You can also find it in your Marketplace account messages.</p><h2>If you've submitted a paper application</h2><p>If you complete a paper application, or an agent, broker, insurance company, or the Marketplace Call Center helps you submit an application, we'll create an application ID for you.</p><p>You\u2019ll need your application ID to view your application on HealthCare.gov. You can start the process by <a href=\"https://www.healthcare.gov/create-account\">creating an account</a>.</p>",
  "url": "/help/how-do-i-find-my-app-id",
